description: This common Yulenka purrs with a rating of 32, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 96, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, Box for East, Stringalong for South, and Stringalong for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [96 Votes, Common]
